 Test Plan for Real-Time Sensor Updates & Alerts Panel

 1. Verify real-time sensor data updates via WebSocket
- Type: Functional / Integration
- Automatable: Yes 

 2. Validate error alert displayed when WebSocket disconnects
- Type: Integration / Negative
- Automatable: Yes

3. Verify clicking alert expands full details modal
- Type: UI
- Automatable: Yes

4. Verify vessel warning are displayed correctly
- Type: UI
- Automatable: Yes

5. Verify low battery notifications are displayed when battery is around a low value
- Type: UI
- Automatable: Yes
